# Assets Leases Impairment Amount

## identifier
de7812

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of provisions for impairment in relation to finance leases receivable as at the relevant date as determined in accordance with the accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Assets.LeasesImpairment.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.06
- period=instant
